name: Rare Stogg
description: What does the all-seeing Rare Stogg perceive with those glorious peepers, you may ask? A shining symphony of sound waves and light, more beautiful than anything its Common cousins could imagine. In an effort to share its experience, Rare Stoggs have taken to creating abstract illustrations using bioluminescent paints.
breedingTime: Breeding Time: 13 hr 30 min, Enhanced Time: 10 hr 7 min 30 sec
